<p>In this week&#8217;s installment of The Proactive Employer Podcast, we&#8217;ll be discussing the Dukes v. Wal-Mart case and its implications for employment class action litigation. We&#8217;ll also be talking about the importance of being a proactive employer when it comes to managing your risk of employment litigation.
